c: 9
v: 61
t: "Among them (the hypocrites) are those who hurt the Prophet and say (of him): \"He is all ear (listening to everyone and disposed to believe them).\" Say: \"Yes, he is all ear, listening to what is best for you; he believes in God, and trusts the believers, and a great mercy for those among you who believe.\" Those who hurt God’s Messenger – for them is a painful punishment"